  <sentence id="s75">
   <tok>
    <orth>jest</orth>
    <lex disamb="1"><base>być</base><ctag>fin:sg:ter:imperf</ctag></lex>
   </tok>
   <tok>
    <orth>to</orth>

  <sentence id="s82">
   <tok>
    <orth>i</orth>

 <chunk id="ch265" type="p">
  <sentence id="s265">

  <sentence id="s509">
